<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623264>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Type series of Cyrtodactylus septimontium sp. nov. from left to right: Top: holotype LSUHC 12484, paratypes LSUHC 8243-44, 12485-86, 12488, 12487. Middle: NAP 05276-77, 05275, 05274, 05273, 05272. Bottom: paratypes NAP 05321, 05320, 05322, 05324, 05323, 05323." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623266>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Cyrtodactylus septimontium sp. nov. Top: adult male (Holotype LSUHC 12484) from Nui Cam Mountain, An Giang province, Vietnam (photo by Ngo Van Tri). Middle: adult female from Nui Cam Mountain, An Giang Province, Vietnam (photo by Nikolay A. Poyarkov). Bottom: Granite boulder forest microhabitat from the slopes of Nui Cam Mountain (photo by L. Grismer)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623234>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Principal component analysis (PCA) of the species of the Cyrtodactylus intermedius complex showing ordination along the first two principal components." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623234/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

